monthly mean precipitation from GPCP:
/data/zhuowang/b/zhuowang/Data/GPCP/precip.mon.mean.nc

monthly mean zonal wind (uwnd) and relative humidity (rhum) from NCEP/DOE reanalysis:
/data/zhuowang/b/zhuowang/Data/NNR2/monthly/uwnd.mon.mean.nc
/data/zhuowang/b/zhuowang/Data/NNR2/monthly/rhum.mon.mean.nc
*Note that the uwnd and rhum are available at different pressure levels and are thus 3D data (x, y, p).
